These files are already heavily tested in Cinder and Nova. Does it make a lot of sense to test them also in Glance? My thinking is that since they are going to be moved to Oslo anytime soon, it is just a matter of weeks before we get rid of it in Glance. They are tested through the vmware store functional tests anyway.

Let me know what you think.

Thanks
